comments[4]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-23T04:55:09.217Z",codex-root,"This is distinct from hac-l25p: extension/tool provisioning passed; failure occurred after the candidate version was applied during the test gate."
  "2026-07-23T05:07:43.242Z",codex-root,A detached worktree candidate bump to 2099.12.31 passed the CLI test and version check. Full repository candidate verification follows after the implementation commit.
  "2026-07-23T05:13:52.742Z",codex-root,PM linked-test execution correctly exposed an invalid cross-repository scripts/run-tests.mjs path added during evidence linking. The nonexistent path was removed and the repository-native Vitest command remains authoritative.
  "2026-07-23T05:20:09.582Z",codex-root,"Decisive acceptance passed on committed head 03dbae9 in a detached worktree after applying synthetic candidate 2099.12.31: 1209 tests and 112 suites passed; coverage was 4467 of 4467 statements 2192 of 2192 branches 897 of 897 functions and 4115 of 4115 lines; audit PM Trivy history secret packaging and commit gates passed. No publication occurred."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-23T04:55:09.217Z",codex-root,Keep dry-run and PR verification non-publishing; use temporary worktree or reversible apply evidence.
learnings[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-23T04:55:09.217Z",codex-root,"Release tests must assert invariants across candidate mutation,not literals from the previously published version."
  "2026-07-23T05:13:52.742Z",codex-root,Never copy a test-runner path from a sibling CLI; validate linked commands through pm test before closure.
