close_reason: The scheduled candidate-version regression is fixed and a fully mutated synthetic candidate passed the complete production release verifier.
body: "## Reproduction\n\nRun the non-dry release pipeline on a clean checkout with release-relevant commits after the last tag. version.mjs applies the daily candidate before release:verify, so a test literal tied to the previous release fails despite package.json and src/cli.ts matching.\n\n## GitHub evidence\n\nIssue #65 and Actions run 29894187971 on merged head 27187f3."
